arStrings.szText:
Merged in Gaping Crevasse in southern Kehjistan with Shard of Agony to summon a powerful enemy. Requires {c_number}2{/c}. Acquired from Malignant Burrow in World Tier 4: Torment only by the one who performs the summoning. 

Drops randomly from World Bosses.
A powerful, nascent being wriggles within.
